
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Course Cards</title>

<style>

*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
}

body{
    background:#f4f4f4;
    font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
}

.card-container{
    display:flex;
    justify-content:center;
    align-items:center;
    flex-wrap:wrap;
    gap:25px;
    padding:50px 20px;
}

.card{
    width:320px;
    background:white;
    border-radius:15px;
    overflow:hidden;
    box-shadow:0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    transition:0.4s;
}

.card:hover{
    transform:translateY(-10px);
    box-shadow:0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
}

.card img{
    width:100%;
    height:200px;
    object-fit:cover;
}

.card-body{
    padding:20px;
}

.card-title{
    font-size:28px;
    text-align:center;
    margin-bottom:10px;
    color:#333;
}

.card-desc{
    text-align:justify;
    line-height:1.6;
    color:#555;
}

.btn{
    display:block;
    width:120px;
    margin:20px auto 0;
    padding:10px;
    border:none;
    border-radius:8px;
    background:#761f86;
    color:white;
    cursor:pointer;
    font-size:16px;
}

.btn:hover{
    background:#5c1768;
}

</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="card-container">

    <!-- Card 1 -->
    <div class="card">
        <img src="https://picsum.photos/400/250?random=1" alt="">
        <div class="card-body">
            <h2 class="card-title">Python</h2>
            <p class="card-desc">
                Python একটি জনপ্রিয় Programming Language। Web Development,
                AI, Machine Learning এবং Automation-এর জন্য ব্যাপকভাবে ব্যবহৃত হয়।
            </p>
            <button class="btn">Learn More</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Card 2 -->
    <div class="card">
        <img src="https://picsum.photos/400/250?random=2" alt="">
        <div class="card-body">
            <h2 class="card-title">HTML & CSS</h2>
            <p class="card-desc">
                HTML ও CSS ব্যবহার করে সুন্দর Website Design করা যায়।
                Frontend Development-এর ভিত্তি হলো HTML এবং CSS।
            </p>
            <button class="btn">Learn More</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Card 3 -->
    <div class="card">
        <img src="https://picsum.photos/400/250?random=3" alt="">
        <div class="card-body">
            <h2 class="card-title">JavaScript</h2>
            <p class="card-desc">
                JavaScript Website-এ Dynamic Feature যোগ করে।
                এটি Frontend এবং Backend উভয় ক্ষেত্রেই ব্যবহার করা হয়।
            </p>
            <button class="btn">Learn More</button>
        </div>
    </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
